HEADWORD: Trichinize
<hw>Trich"i*nize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To render
trichinous; to affect with trichinae; -- chiefly used in the past
participle; <as>as, <ex>trichinized</ex> pork</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

